Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.81,0:00:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但愿…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但愿你能成为我的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,妻子？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要我成为您的妻子？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.15,0:00:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.34,0:00:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.97,0:00:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,恕我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.17,0:00:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会笑得这么开心啊
